Blitz Basic 2.1 Ordering Details
================================
      
UK and European Users:
----------------------

If you are a registered Blitz user, you can upgrade to the new manual
and get an additional disk containing the latest Teditor, Debugger
and some exclusive source code for £14.99.

If you are a new user you can purchase the new manual and disks
for £24.99.
  
Please note: The full retail price released to the high street on
             13/12/95 will be £34.99.

  Payment can be made by cheque to:

    Acid Software 
    Guildhall Leisure Services Limited
    Unit 15, Guildhall Industrial Estate
    Kirk Sandall
    Doncaster DN3 1QR
    UK

  Payment by Credit Card can be made over the phone:

    UK: 01302 890000
    Outside UK: +44 1302 890000

  Please ask for Maureen or Sheila, and if you are a
  registered user please quote your Blitz User 
  registration number.

All prices include postage and packaging. Please allow up to
two weeks for delivery.
For further information email Ted@blitzuk.demon.co.uk


American and Australasian Users:
--------------------------------

Please contact Acid Software in New Zealand via fax on
+649 358 5325 or email at acid@iconz.co.nz. We will be able to
advise on pricing and will be happy to accept your credit card
details.
